name: Lejos code
body:
### Project
This project has as a goal to contain code that may be useful by others. The repository contains code written using the lejos library for controlling lego mindstorms robots.

### Authors and Contributors
My name is Kjetil Fjellheim and in this is my personal lejos code repository.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with setup just let me knoe and I`ll try to help.
